      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "that makes sense, but i'm still a bit lost on how the actual pattern works. like, why does it go in a circle? and is there a specific rule for how to remember if i should be looking for sharps or flats when i move around it? it feels a bit random right now.",
